messages.text: Want to trade pics?
Um, how about, no!
Why not?
Because I don’t know who you are.
Creeper much.
Now that’s not very nice.
And you’re not very weird. Not at all.
How did you get this number anyway???
A mutual friend.
And who’s that?
Oh, so now you want something from me? Looks like you’re into trading after all.
Is this Luke? :P
Nope.
This is Garrett isn’t it??? You’re just evil enough to be Garrett. ;)
Not, Garrett.
Kaitlyn thinks you’re, Noah? Is this Noah?
Who’s Kaitlyn?
My bestie. She’s right here beside me.
...I see.
So that tells me you’re not Noah. Noah, would know Kaitlyn.
Maybe I’m lying. Maybe I’m trying to throw you off. Keep you guessing.
Whatever. I’m still not giving you a pic.
Well, in all fairness, I did say trade, didn’t I…
Yep. Send me YOUR pic! :)
But I asked you first.
So!?!
What if I earned your picture?
What do you mean?
I mean, what if I did something that would earn a pic of you?
What do you say?
Are you still there?
Depends on what it is, I guess.
Who IS this? :)
I know! You ask me a question about yourself and I’ll do my best to guess the right answer. Sound fair?
Alright. How much do I weigh?
Tough one. You’re not going to make this easy are you?
Lol. How MUCH do I weigh?
105 pounds wet.
Haha. You are incorrect, sir!
Give me one more chance?
Ok. What color is my hair?
Hmm. Blonde.
Damn. You got it.
But that was too easy. Lots of girls have blonde hair.
Okay. I see your point.
How about, if I guessed what you’re wearing?
Creeper alert!
Seriously. If I get it right, you owe me a picture?
Ok. Sure. Go for it.
Hmmm. Let me see.
Little black shorts and a white shirt?
NOT FUNNY. WHO IS THIS?
Looks like you owe me a picture, Bailey.
Again, not very nice.
You’re going to hurt my feelings.
I’m blocking you!
But I still want a pic.
No.
A real good one.
I’m through playing your game.
But I’ve earned it, Bailey.
Who put you up to this?
C’mon. Let me guess again.
How about I guess what you're doing right now? Like at this very moment.
I don’t like this.
What’s not to like. I think this is fun.
Ok. I’m ready. What am I doing right now?
Wow. You really pulled out all the stops.
You’re doing a kung fu pose on top of a giant stuffed dinosaur?
IM CALLING THE POLICE. HOW CAN YOU SEE ME?
You owe me a pic.
NO WAY!
How are you doing this? Do you have a camera in my bedroom?
Alright. I guess I can let you in on it now.
Kaitlyn, she’s been telling me what to say. I’d ask you a question, and she would text me the correct answer.
I’m going to kill her! That was sooo creepy. haha.
Sorry, if I frightened you.
Great prank, tho!
She thought it would be funny to see what you do. So, how about that pic?
… Wait.
She wasn’t in here during the last guess?
Where was she?
She went to the kitchen. She was hungry.
LOL. You caught me.
Caught you? wtf?
You know, you’re right. I’m not being fair.
I need to share a pic with you.
That’s my house!
You owe me a pic, Bailey.
I’m calling the police, right now.
Are you going to make me come in there and take my own pic of you?
Stop this. Why are you doing this?
Kaitlyn wouldn’t send me a pic either.
So I had to take my own. Want to see it?
NO. I don’t want to see anything.
You owe me a pic, Bailey?
That’s two now that I’ve given you. We’re trading, right?
You owe me a pic.
Aw, there you go, but not good enough.
You’ve gone and made yourself all messy.
LEAVE ME ALONE!
THE POLICE ARE COMING
THEY ARE ON THEIR WAY RIGHT NOW!!!
Okay. I see how it is.
Another trade then.
Stop this, please!
That’s three, Bailey. You know what they say about three strikes.
I have a gun!
LOL
No you don’t.
I sent you a pic. You got what you wanted.
I want a good one.
I want one to remember you by.
Forever.
You’ll have to better than that.
STAY AWAY FROM ME!
I’ve collected lot’s of pics. Really nice ones.
You know, I bet you’d like to see a few.
She was afraid of the water going up her nose. Isn’t that funny?
This one thought I was a friend.
She had the brightest blonde hair.
Okay, Bailey. Last pic I’m going to trade… and I’ve been more than generous.
Oh, I really like this one.
You’re still on chat, Bailey.
Unlock the door, Bailey.
Are you ready?
PLEASE DON’T!!!
It’s time for your close up.
Ok. I have a pic for you. A good one.
It’s too late, Bailey.
I’m sending it now.
… I’m waiting …
You guessed wrong.
lost connection
